<item>
            <title>[LU-9271] sanity-scrub test_5 fails with &apos;(17) Expected &apos;scanning&apos; on mds2&apos; </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9271</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity-scrub test 5 fails with&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Update not seen after 6s: wanted &apos;scanning&apos; got &apos;failed&apos;
 sanity-scrub test_5: @@@@@@ FAIL: (17) Expected &apos;scanning&apos; on mds2 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Comparing the console log on mds2 for the failed run and a successful run, one difference is the following error messages found at the end of the console log for the failed run:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;05:55:09:[12426.357734] LustreError: 18029:0:(llog_cat.c:260:llog_cat_id2handle()) lustre-MDT0000-osp-MDT0001: error opening log id 0x2:1025:0: rc = -2
05:55:09:[12426.362523] LustreError: 18029:0:(llog_cat.c:793:llog_cat_process_cb()) lustre-MDT0000-osp-MDT0001: cannot find handle for llog 0x2:1025: -2
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So far, this test is failing only in review-dne-part-2 test sessions.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This test has failed with this error 7 times since March 24 of this year:&lt;br/&gt;
2017-03-28 - &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/7623aa64-13a6-11e7-8920-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/7623aa64-13a6-11e7-8920-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
